==English==

===Noun===

'''fascination'''

#The act of [[fascinate|fascinating]], [[bewhich]]ing, or [[enchant]]ing; [[enchantment]]; [[witchcraft]]; the exercise of a powerful or irresistible influence on the affections or passions; unseen, inexplicable influence.
#The state or condition of being fascinated.
#That which fascinates; a charm; a spell.

